1. write functions for a full burger meal: 

function makeBurger (cheese , onions) {
Add bun
Add cheese
Add onions
Add burger_patty
Add bun
}

function makeSideMeal (chicken , bread_crumbs , salt) {
Put chicken in yolk
Put chicken in bread_crumbs
Add salt
Fry chicken
}

function makeSoftDrink (pepsi , regular) {
Add regular_size_cardboard_cup
Fill in water_450ml
Fill in pepsi_syrup_50ml
Add regular_size_cardboard_cup_lid
}

