2. create a program/recipe for a fruit salad,  using examples of all 3 operator groups

function make_fruit_salad ( ingridient0 , ingridient1 , ingridient2 )
ingridients:
( condensed milk = ingridient0 )
( pineapples = ingridient1 )
( strawberries = ingridient2 )
{
fruit_salad = ingridient0 + ingridient1 + ingridient2
if ingridient1 < ingridient2 make ingridient2 = ingridient1
if ingridient1 > ingridient2 make ingridient1 = ingridient2
}

